Enhance an Artifact to Get a Passive

Tap Enhance on the Enhancements screen to view the interface for enhancing gear.
Next tap the Artifact tab.
Tap the artifact you'd like to enhance, and then select the materials you'll use to enhance it.
After three limit breaks, and maxing out the artifact's level, you'll obtain a passive ability.
Go to a character's Passive Abilities screen to equip the passive abilities you obtain.

You can get artifacts in the World of Illusions: Treasure Hunt and Radiant Artifacts quests.
